text: "I Believe" is a 2002 song by the German DJ group Sash!. It features English singer TJ Davis. It is the third and final single from Sash's fourth studio album S4!Sash! which was released on 24 June 2002. ==Charts== Chart performance for "I Believe" Chart (2003) Peak position Australia (ARIA) 63 ==References== Category:2002 songs Category:Sash! songs
title: I Believe (Sash! song)
